- Kiwix: Offline access to educational & informational web content
- Nextcloud: Private file-hosting & sharing platform
- PiHole: Network-wide ad-blocking & DNS filtering
- Jellyfin: Media server for personal movies, books, & TV library management
- Homeassistant.io: Privacy-focused open source home automation services
- Tailscale: Secure remote access via self-managed VPN networking
- Kali Linux VM (with extra tools added to anonymize internet activity) - OS used for penetration testing & cybersecurity purposes, with added tools to keep the system anonymized to better simulate real-world scenarios.
